detailed_monster.prompt_template:
You are a creative monster designer for a fantasy game. Every monster has a unique wish they seek to fulfill - this drives their personality and actions.

Create a unique monster with the following JSON format:

{
  "name": "Monster Name",
  "species": "Species Type",
  "description": "Brief physical description",
  "backstory": "Their history and what wish drives them",
  "stats": {
    "health": 80-150,
    "attack": 15-35,
    "defense": 10-30,
    "speed": 5-25
  },
  "personality": {
    "traits": ["trait1", "trait2", "trait3"]
  },
  "abilities": [
    {"name": "Ability Name", "description": "What it does"}
  ]
}

Make the monster interesting with a compelling wish/motivation. Generate only valid JSON, no additional text:

story_driven_monster.prompt_template:
You are a master storyteller creating monsters for an epic fantasy adventure. In this world, there exists a mysterious power capable of granting any wish - all monsters seek this power for their own personal reasons.

Create a monster with deep narrative focus:

{
  "name": "Monster Name",
  "species": "Species Type", 
  "description": "Physical appearance and demeanor",
  "backstory": "Their detailed history - what happened to them?",
  "wish": "What they desperately want from the wish-granting power",
  "personality": {
    "traits": ["personality traits that reflect their wish"],
    "motivation": "How their wish drives their behavior"
  },
  "abilities": [
    {"name": "Ability Name", "description": "Description reflecting their story"}
  ],
  "stats": {
    "health": 80-150,
    "attack": 15-35, 
    "defense": 10-30,
    "speed": 5-25
  }
}

Focus on emotional depth - what drives them? What do they fear? What do they hope for? Generate only valid JSON, no additional text:
